<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN"><html> <head> <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"> <meta name="referrer" content="no-referrer"> <title> Web Filter Violation </title> <style type="text/css"> html, body, div { padding: 0; margin: 0; font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 21px; } div.header { background-image: linear-gradient(rgb(255,0,0,0), rgb(59, 200, 192)); 0 0 no-repeat; padding: 20px; text-align: center; display: block; } .header img { max-width: 150px; height: auto; } div.header h1 { background: url('data:image/png;base64, ') 0 0 no-repeat; margin-left: 40%; margin-right: 40%; margin-top: 8px; display: block; width: 50%; align: center; text-indent: -9999; } .converge_logo { background-image: url('data:image/png;base64, '); background-position: center; background-size: 100% 100%; max-width: 200px; height: 60px; margin: 0 auto; } div.content { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; border: 1px solid #f2f2f2; padding: 40px; margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; } .blocked h3 { color: #c00; font-size: 50px; line-height: 41px; padding: 0; margin: 0; } .authenticate h3 { color: #36c; } div.main h3 { } ul { text-align: left; width: auto; margin: 0 auto; display: inline-block; } ul li { list-style: none; } .warning_logo { background-image: url('data:image/png;base64, '); background-position: center; background-size: 100% 100%; width: 50px; height: 50px; margin-right: 20px; display: inline-block; position: relative; top: -20px; } </style> </head> <body class="blocked"> <div class="header"> <div alt="converge_logo" class="converge_logo"> &nbsp; </div> </div> <div class="content"> <div class="main"> <h3> <div class="warning_logo"> &nbsp; </div> SYSTEM ALERT! </h3> <div class="notice"> <p> You have tried to access a web page which is in violation of your internet usage policy. </p> <ul> <li> Category: <b> Unrated </b> </li> <li> User name: <b>  </b> </li> <li> Group name: <b>  </b> </li> </ul> <p style="color: #FF0000;"> <b> ADVISORY: PERMISSION IS NEEDED TO ACCESS THIS SITE; SEEK THE APPROVAL OF YOUR IMMEDIATE HEAD </b> </p> <p> For other queries and concerns, please do not hesitate to contact IT Helpdesk at <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/?fs=1&to=ithelpdesk@convergeict.com&tf=cm&su=REQUEST_ACCESS"> <b> ithelpdesk@convergeict.com </b> </a> </p> </div> </div> </div> </body></html>
